== 改善工程 ==
[[橫貫鐵路|橫貫鐵路]]停靠伊靈大道站，預計2018年起投入服務<ref name="Crossrail 2018">{{cite news | url=https://www.google.com/hostednews/ukpress/article/ALeqM5gKH5fiQT63-FLo6vMfXKorAteqrA?docId=B308521287593766A00 | title=Capital's key services protected, says Johnson | publisher=The Press Association | date=20 October 2010 | accessdate=21 October 2010 | archive-date=2020-03-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326093707/https://www.google.com/hostednews/ukpress/article/ALeqM5gKH5fiQT63-FLo6vMfXKorAteqrA?docId=B308521287593766A00 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。為了容納橫貫鐵路列車，[[英國國營鐵路公司|英國國營鐵路公司]]將進行以下改動：
