* 無障礙化<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.tfl.gov.uk/travel-information/improvements-and-projects/step-free-access |title=Step-free Access - Transport for London |accessdate=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2015-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205100713/https://www.tfl.gov.uk/travel-information/improvements-and-projects/step-free-access |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 擴建票務廳，增建閘機
* 車站東端興建新天橋，連接1至4號月台
* 4號月台興建新遮陽蓬<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ealinggazette.co.uk/ealing-news/local-ealing-news/2009/10/07/boris-faces-calls-to-improve-ealing-station-64767-24878287/|work=Ealing Gazette|publisher=Trinity Mirror|title=Boris faces calls to improve Ealing Station|first=Michael|last=Russell|date=7 October 2009|accessdate=2017-12-15|archive-date=2011-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810042805/http://www.ealinggazette.co.uk/ealing-news/local-ealing-news/2009/10/07/boris-faces-calls-to-improve-ealing-station-64767-24878287/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crossrail.co.uk/news/press-releases/crossrail-station-design-contract-awarded-network-rail-release#.T7AJqsWaU08|accessdate=13 May 2012|date=17 May 2011|title=Crossrail Station Design Contract Awarded|publisher=Crossrail|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025114952/http://www.crossrail.co.uk/news/press-releases/crossrail-station-design-contract-awarded-network-rail-release#.T7AJqsWaU08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.crossrail.co.uk/assets/download/636|accessdate=13 May 2012|publisher=Crossrail|title=Chapter 22 Route window W5 Ealing Broadway station}}</ref>
